**Story**

Once upon a  time, in a forest , there lived a money who resided on a jamun tree, which was on the ban of a river.
In the same forest, there lived a crocodile and his wife.
One day the crocodilecame to the banks of the river and rested under the tree.The Kindhearted monkey offered him some fruitd.
The crocodile came back the next day for more fruits , as he loved them.
As days passed by, the crocodile and monkey became best friends